%p Hello #{@resource.email},

%p Someone has requested a link to change your password. You can do this through the button below.

%p= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), style: 'display: inline-block; background-color: #007bff; color: #ffffff; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;'

%p{ style: 'margin-top: 24px;' } If you didn't request this, please ignore this email. Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.

%p
  Best regards,
  %br
  The Corsego Team

%p{ style: 'font-size: 12px; color: #6c757d;' }= link_to 'Visit Corsego', root_url
